  <h3>Customizing the Default View for a Console</h3> 
  <p>You can customize the default view (column, card, list) for a console:</p> 
  <ol> 
   <li><p>You can reorder the views by overlaying the required entry from under:</p>  <p>The first entry will be the default.</p> <p>The nodes available correlate to the view options in the rail:</p> 
    <ul> 
     <li><span class="code">column</span></li> 
     <li><span class="code">card</span></li> 
     <li><span class="code">list</span></li> 
    </ul> </li> 
   <li><p>For example, in a overlay for list:</p>  <p>Define the following property:</p> 
    <ul> 
     <li><strong>Name</strong>: <span class="code">sling:orderBefore</span></li> 
     <li><strong>Type</strong>: <span class="code">String</span><br /> </li> 
     <li><strong>Value</strong>: <span class="code">column</span></li> 
